data.description: MOVE IN READY! Get ready to fall in love! Beautiful and cozy only begin to describe this home with new paint all throughout! Kitchen counters and almost all flooring is new! Near shopping and restaurants, but still tucked away from busy main streets. Large, fenced backyard boasts mature pecan trees and a workshop/covered patio area. You don't want to miss your chance to see this gem, call your favorite broker today for a showing!
